@post_election
on-arrival: {!
// set congress proportion to votes
Q.pps_r = Q.pps_votes;
Q.bbwr_r = Q.bbwr_votes;
Q.pschd_r = Q.pschd_votes;
Q.npr_r = Q.npr_votes;
Q.kpp_r = Q.kpp_votes;
Q.pslw_r = Q.pslw_votes;
Q.pslp_r = Q.pslp_votes;
Q.sn_r = Q.sn_votes;
Q.owp_r = Q.owp_votes;
Q.other_r = Q.other_votes;


// The largest party can only be the OWP or the BBWR.
Q.largest_party = 'BBWR';
if (Q.owp_r >= Q.bbwr_r && Q.owp_r >= Q.kpp_r) {
    Q.largest_party = 'OWP';
}
if (Q.kpp_r >= Q.bbwr_r && Q.kpp_r >= Q.owp_r) {
    Q.largest_party = 'KPP';
}

// coalitions
Q.weimar_coalition = Q.bbwr_r + Q.pslw_r + Q.pschd_r - 3;
Q.grand_coalition = Q.bbwr_r + Q.pslw_r + Q.pschd_r + Q.pslp_r;
Q.bourgeois_coalition = Q.pslw_r + Q.pschd_r + Q.pslp_r + Q.other_r;
Q.center_right_coalition = Q.pschd_r + Q.pslw_r + Q.pslp_r + Q.other_r + Q.sn_r;
Q.right_coalition = Q.pschd_r + Q.pslp_r + Q.other_r + Q.sn_r;
Q.far_right_coalition = Q.sn_r + Q.owp_r;
Q.left_coalition = Q.bbwr_r + Q.kpp_r;
// this is an absurd concept lol
Q.united_front_coalition = Q.bbwr_r + Q.kpp_r + Q.pschd_r + Q.pslw_r - 3;
Q.anti_democratic_coalition = Q.kpp_r + Q.owp_r;
// aka everyone except nazi, kpp, sn
Q.neo_weimar_coalition = Q.bbwr_r + Q.pslw_r + Q.pschd_r + Q.pslp_r + Q.other_r;
!}

The electoral system is essentially proportional, with the proportion of Reichstag seats roughly equal to the proportion of votes.
 
**Election results:**

# 1928: 30, 1930: 25, 1932: 22
BBWR: [+ bbwr_r +]

# 1928: 15, 1930: 15, 1932: 
PSCHD + NPR: [+ pschd_r +]

# 1928: 10, 1930: 13
KPP: [+ kpp_r +]

# 1928: 5, 1930: 4 (as DstP)
PSL-W: [+ pslw_r +]

# 1928: 9, 1930: 5
PSL-P: [+ pslp_r +]

# 1928: 14, 1930: 7
SN: [+ sn_r +]

# 1928: 3, 1930: 18
OWP: [+ owp_r +]

# 1928: 9, 1930: 10
Other: [+ other_r +]

# 1927: TODO
PPS: [+ pps_r +]

# 1927: TODO
NPR: [+ npr_r +]

**Potential coalitions:**

Weimar Coalition (BBWR + PSCHD + PSL-W): [+ weimar_coalition +]

Grand Coalition (BBWR + PSCHD + NPR + PSL-W + PSL-P): [+ grand_coalition +]

Bourgeois Coalition (PSCHD + NPR + PSL-W + PSL-P + Others): [+ bourgeois_coalition +]

Right-wing Coalition (PSCHD + NPR + PSL-P + Others + SN): [+ right_coalition +]

